    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Pen<hi rend="sup">a</hi></placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>
                <date>Nov. 21st</date>
            </p>
            <p>My Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">It becomes my pleasing duty to address<lb/> you (as Secretary of a
                religious society of this place)<lb/> and to enclose the Preamble &amp; resolution
                adopted<lb/> by said society with the <add>?</add> desire that<lb/> they should
                receive a place in your valuable journal</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">It was our will to give this publicity thro' your<lb/> interesting
                periodical before it appear'd to the world<lb/> thro' any other medium. but some of
                our friends<lb/> were fearful we would be too late for insertion by<lb/> you this
                month and without my knowledge or instru<lb/>mentality I found it published in the
                “Carrier” of this<lb/> city. I lose no time in forwarding the same to<lb/> you with
                the hope that you will give us a place<lb/> at your earliest convenience.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">We very much regretted that circumstances<lb/> prevented our seeing
                yourself and several valued<lb/> friends on our return thro'
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> we could not<lb/> remain long enough to do
                so.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">With the hope that we may soon<add>?</add> meet<add>?</add><lb/> and
                that <placeName>Charleston</placeName> may again boast of you among<lb/> its
                visitors</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I am Dr Sir truly your friend &amp; well wisher</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Caroline A Moise</persName>
            </p>
            <p>My husband &amp; daughters kindest regards</p>
        </body>
    </text>
